Doc: The unit in which a commission is denominated.

Source.Contents:
/#
 The unit in which a commission is denominated.
 #/
enum FpML5.transparency.CommissionDenominationEnum {
    # The commission is expressed in basis points, in reference to the price referenced in the document.
    BPS 
    # The commission is expressed as a percentage of the gross price referenced in the document.
    Percentage 
    # The commission is expressed in cents per share.
    CentsPerShare 
    # The commission is expressed as a absolute amount.
    FixedAmount 

}

BPS.Doc: The commission is expressed in basis points, in reference to the price referenced in the document.
BPS.Name: BPS

Percentage.Doc: The commission is expressed as a percentage of the gross price referenced in the document.
Percentage.Name: Percentage

CentsPerShare.Doc: The commission is expressed in cents per share.
CentsPerShare.Name: CentsPerShare

FixedAmount.Doc: The commission is expressed as a absolute amount.
FixedAmount.Name: FixedAmount
